  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4517f0f2d9beae5f415511feb6aa0a79.avif?t=1741917351\" width=608 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Play your way with a variety of builds, weapons, and perks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ►Each new run comes with randomized options!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/bdcc68f31ea2297afd4bfe8b0511319d.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/bdcc68f31ea2297afd4bfe8b0511319d.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/bdcc68f31ea2297afd4bfe8b0511319d.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ A comfortable horde shooter that is easy to pick up and play with 15 minute sessions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4ce25854406301b631e7c66887bebad6.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4ce25854406301b631e7c66887bebad6.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4ce25854406301b631e7c66887bebad6.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Lovely artwork by @Holy Potion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4b12284685af2788c6c92d03aa69cb10.avif?t=1741917351\" width=600 height=339 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/a7f6d6ed23153387584f45e18a0e04f8.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/a7f6d6ed23153387584f45e18a0e04f8.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/a7f6d6ed23153387584f45e18a0e04f8.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/16311f44c887084b85cd69114f851f3f.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/16311f44c887084b85cd69114f851f3f.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/16311f44c887084b85cd69114f851f3f.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/8a924249e3a44cdaaa499cbf18d3358c.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/8a924249e3a44cdaaa499cbf18d3358c.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/8a924249e3a44cdaaa499cbf18d3358c.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Synopsis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ► In 2080, corrupt corporations effectively run everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three major corporations attempted to crack into the hacker group Rinascita's hidden server but failed to gain access.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fueled by a plea from a email, X, the group's greatest code cracker, sets out to break into each corporation's servers to dig up any useful information. Rinascita's other members will provide support and help X uncover the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terms of Services : </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4517f0f2d9beae5f415511feb6aa0a79.avif?t=1741917351\" width=608 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Play your way with a variety of builds, weapons, and perks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ►Each new run comes with randomized options!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/bdcc68f31ea2297afd4bfe8b0511319d.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/bdcc68f31ea2297afd4bfe8b0511319d.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/bdcc68f31ea2297afd4bfe8b0511319d.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ A comfortable horde shooter that is easy to pick up and play with 15 minute sessions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4ce25854406301b631e7c66887bebad6.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4ce25854406301b631e7c66887bebad6.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4ce25854406301b631e7c66887bebad6.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Lovely artwork by @Holy Potion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/4b12284685af2788c6c92d03aa69cb10.avif?t=1741917351\" width=600 height=339 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/a7f6d6ed23153387584f45e18a0e04f8.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/a7f6d6ed23153387584f45e18a0e04f8.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/a7f6d6ed23153387584f45e18a0e04f8.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/16311f44c887084b85cd69114f851f3f.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/16311f44c887084b85cd69114f851f3f.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/16311f44c887084b85cd69114f851f3f.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/8a924249e3a44cdaaa499cbf18d3358c.poster.avif?t=1741917351\" width=594 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/8a924249e3a44cdaaa499cbf18d3358c.webm?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090760/extras/8a924249e3a44cdaaa499cbf18d3358c.mp4?t=1741917351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Synopsis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ► In 2080, corrupt corporations effectively run everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three major corporations attempted to crack into the hacker group Rinascita's hidden server but failed to gain access.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fueled by a plea from a email, X, the group's greatest code cracker, sets out to break into each corporation's servers to dig up any useful information. Rinascita's other members will provide support and help X uncover the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terms of Services : </p>",
